Asked about the club appointing a director of football figure, Wenger said: &ldquo;No. I don&rsquo;t know what director of football means. Is it somebody who stands in the road and directs play right and left? I don&rsquo;t understand and I never did understand what it means.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
It was then put to him that there might be some restructuring. &ldquo;No, no, no,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;Sorry, no. I&rsquo;m not prepared to talk about that. I&rsquo;m the manager of Arsenal Football Club and, as long as I&rsquo;m manager of Arsenal Football Club, I<span style="color: red;"> will decide what happens on the technical front. That&rsquo;s it.</span>&rdquo;
